snippet.title: Yoshi's Cookie (Game Boy) Gameplay
snippet.description:
The goal of Yoshi's Cookie is to line up all the cookies in a horizontal or in a vertical order. If there is none left in a stage, the stage is complete. This game has 10 rounds and each round has 10 stages. 100 stages to complete.
